      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "POKER NISMO (5) showed little early speed at her last couple, the latest finishing fourth (22.87) in a Grade 5 at Maitland. Better than last start and worth following up. ZUMA ZESTA (2) turned spotting a big start finishing sixth (24.05) last time in a Grade 5 at this track. Cannot be left out. HOOKED ON HOPE (7) was below best at her last start when 6th at this track following a third place finish (22.66) at Gosford two back. Has a good record here at this journey. Good beginner but will need a little luck early crossing from an outside draw. One of the better hopes. RAINING WINE (1) was unplaced here last start but gets her chance to atone.",
